    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>What is this forgotten world?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134960/extras/920d987ffb63beb698c0eaf350a4d2d1.poster.avif?t=1755316441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134960/extras/920d987ffb63beb698c0eaf350a4d2d1.webm?t=1755316441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134960/extras/920d987ffb63beb698c0eaf350a4d2d1.mp4?t=1755316441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>You are lost in a strange and unsettling universe. Try to stay sane as you navigate eerie creatures and mysterious places.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles using your ability to possess objects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the secrets of the protagonist’s past as the story unfolds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy adorable pixel art with a dark twist</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134960/extras/5c3d5ac4df57dfa3fbf4244335230256.poster.avif?t=1755316441\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134960/extras/5c3d5ac4df57dfa3fbf4244335230256.webm?t=1755316441\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2134960/extras/5c3d5ac4df57dfa3fbf4244335230256.mp4?t=1755316441\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Don't be afraid of being alone. Be afraid of what’s lurking around you.</p>",
